{
  "stem": "2391.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The first, we had two-- two tests, two exams one year.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the first exam was before Christmas, in-- in winter, and the second one was before the summer vacation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the first exam, I was the best in my class.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had 33 students in the class, and I was the best.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I was already fluent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the teacher came up to my parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I remember-- I still see her and telling them how proud she was of me and how well I did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And at first, I remember, when we learned the alphabet, for instance, and they had these little pictures to make the words.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I could not-- I didn't even know the word, what it means, because I didn't know the language.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I always tried to-- to sneak, you know, at another student to see what they were doing, to-- because I didn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But because I had to, I-- I-- I did it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I had no choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to work harder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Were there other Jewish children going to your school?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, quite a few.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Quite a few.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, in winter, we had this rule that I didn't have to come to school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was excused on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- we had to go to school on Saturday, half a day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you had to prove that you were religious.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you went not religious and you didn't care and you didn't keep the holidays, you had to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Only if you kept the holidays.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I was excused on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, I had to catch up and-- and-- and check out what they were-- what they did, and then, you know, catch up with the-- with the class.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
